{"tid":2164199,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派去留民調周五公佈","createTime":"2020-08-19T05:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T06:34:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f486353b361438b8a57577da88be71db02f6a6e","tid":2164199,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/XNGMELSCSVGQ3PZ3ZVWIXBE44U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FXNGMELSCSVGQ3PZ3ZVWIXBE44U%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInHdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=2c7cedc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FXNGMELSCSVGQ3PZ3ZVWIXBE44U%2F&h=14c25b9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/XNGMELSCSVGQ3PZ3ZVWIXBE44U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民主派去留民調周五公佈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Xc1pAqrdnKuGRNMTYMyAXTKUds8=/6106x4071/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JCMTXIVJBRGSZNNVVAG23QVYHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXc1pAqrdnKuGRNMTYMyAXTKUds8%3D%2F6106x4071%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJCMTXIVJBRGSZNNVVAG23QVYHQ.jpg&h=dc3c2b62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾劍華<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派是否接受立法會延任，民意取態是考慮因素之一，香港民意研究所副行政總裁鍾劍華博士就透露，研究所就泛民留任進行民調，本周五公佈結果，惟鍾同時明言，民調樣本來自「我們香港人」計劃意見群組，非全港性抽樣，故不應被視作民主派決定的唯一理據。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大多數泛民傾向留守立會  黎智英：議員肩負責任擋惡法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾劍華：非全港性 僅供參考<br />\n<br />\n鍾劍華解釋，民意研究所轄下「我們香港人」倡導計劃將民主派立會議員去留問題，選作本周取樣議題，從計劃中約10萬人意見群組取樣，料最終回應人數有最少一萬人，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他又透露，今次民調問題簡單，「其實就係問是否支持總辭定留低」，至於民主派立會議員應否跟從民調結果，鍾認為政治人物作為意見領袖，不一定要跟從民意，「唔會次次係由民意帶住你走，本身自己應該有一套理念去支持你個決定」，惟相信如民意有壓倒性結果，並跟議員決定不相符，「咁佢應該冇得唔回應解釋吧！」鍾又指雖時間緊迫，但仍有時間發起全港性取樣民調，「我就建議如果係做，要盡快說服其他民主派議員參與，快啲開始委託人做。」"},{"pid":"c13ea1c1d21c0a0f20526694743ec420b9460bd0","tid":2164199,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"快啲做全港民調啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇錢就出聲"},{"pid":"4b62bebcc2ee7de91cad80359ef4c7a256f10b91","tid":2164199,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c13ea1c1d21c0a0f20526694743ec420b9460bd0","tid":2164199,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"快啲做全港民調啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇錢就出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"做全港大型公投"},{"pid":"99884ea9b72c7bbd17fb263f1016c7b8dcf25000","tid":2164199,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"佢地會搵藉口架啦"},{"pid":"83010e493c065a6168ceac87ed9e7ce09a001da7","tid":2164199,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所  人大常委決定現屆立法會繼續履行職責不少於一年。你有多支持或反對全體立法會議員繼續出任議員？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2164375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2164375</a>"},{"pid":"8b80128a006881d95bca568c688bee0df031d25c","tid":2164199,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所<br />\n<br />\n人大常委決定現屆立法會繼續履行職責不少於一年。你有多支持或反對全體立法會議員繼續出任議員？<br />\n<br />\n好支持<br />\n幾支持<br />\n一半半<br />\n幾反對<br />\n好反對<br />\n不知道／很難說<br />\n<br />\n==============================================<br />\n<br />\n入去表達民意, 越多人參與越巨參考價值<br />\n<br />\nlink<br />\n香港民意研究所：我們香港人意見組群調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScT2MrW6ittUhdN3_Lj7lmA-M0cunLN7xPrm3bj2zL03-2d7Q/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScT2MrW6ittUhdN3_Lj7lmA-M0cunLN7xPrm3bj2zL03-2d7Q%2Fviewform&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInHdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=d17ba18d\" data-auto-link ta